&lt;p&gt;An adapter board based on &lt;strong&gt;ESP32-C6&lt;/strong&gt; for upgrading ready-made relay modules in the popular “Arduino relay board” form factor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It supports both classic electromechanical relay boards and solid-state relay boards, typically with &lt;strong&gt;2 / 4 / 8 channels&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The idea is simple: replace the stock controller with a compact C6 board, and your old relay module gets modern wireless connectivity: &lt;strong&gt;Wi‑Fi 6, BLE 5, Zigbee / Thread (802.15.4)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>